  "body": "Due to the changes in https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/pull/3637, if a task adds a property to the HRE, this won't be reflected in other tasks. This happen because we are creating a new (modified) HRE between task executions.\r\n\r\nThis breaks Nexus's setup, and it's very likely that it affects other projects too.\r\n\r\nThis is a blocker for the release of v2.13.0.",
